reviews.review_text: Hippy Jerry's Birthday !!! Thanks Hunter ! & all involved.  Happy Jerry's Birthday ! We Can always depend on you. Your Hard work is appreciated more than you know. Grateful 4 always.....
Great Show Great Show, great tape exemplifies the late summer tour of 1982
